c: 5
v: 93
t: "Abo bakholwayo benze izenzo zobulungisa, akukho sono kubo ngenxa yoko bakutya (kwilixa eladlulayo) ukuba bayamoyika uAllâh, bakholwe, benze izenzo ezilungileyo, bathi kwakhona boyike uAllâh bakholwe baphinde kwakhona boyike uAllâh, benze izenzo ezilungileyo. UAllâh Uyabathanda abenzi bokulungileyo"